{"tid":1681521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【 抗 暴 物 資 】 香 港 人 既 物 資 站， 無 物 資 點 出 黎 抗 爭 ？ ！！！！！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-10-29T13:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T11:13:59.000Z","uid":28105,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c475b2552094006ab8cee0a0dfe5eda406ef11fb","tid":1681521,"uid":28105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:09:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>⚠️《多元化》物資站⚠️</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫手推呀，要令每一位手足出到黎都要有足夠裝備生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>TG Channel:<a href=\"https://t.me/Peaceandlovehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FPeaceandlovehk&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2BsgxD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=133e3044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Peaceandlovehk</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Instagram:<a href=\"https://instagram.com/peaceandlovehk?igshid=17gvlktg6vz6b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fpeaceandlovehk%3Figshid%3D17gvlktg6vz6b&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2BsgxD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=d05c99af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/peaceandlovehk?igshid=17gvlktg6vz6b</a></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Facebook:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Peaceandlovehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPeaceandlovehk&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2BsgxD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=b604421c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Peaceandlovehk</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tyUtfpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtyUtfpQ.jpg&h=c4e9b63d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S1niCDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS1niCDb.jpg&h=5afc30f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9UdUVpS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9UdUVpS.jpg&h=f9266ca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">自612開始與前線風雨同路，直到現在物資義工仍在堅守崗位，每次都會出來支援💪🏻。十月一日我們亦無懼tg在前線派發物資👷🏻&zwj;♂️，我們的義工團中有文宣，影音，Fa隊，家長隊，哨兵</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><br />\n‼️我們一直低調行蹤，以保證各義工及手足安全，做到支持前線之餘亦不流血、不送頭！ .<br />\n<br />\n所有物資歡迎各位手足黎任攞‼️‼️‼️</span></span><br />\n<br />\n保護裝備⛑🥽<br />\n⛑防彈頭盔<br />\n🥽眼罩<br />\n🗿面罩<br />\n🐽雙罐本體<br />\n🐽組合濾罐<br />\n🎒防水袋(8升)<br />\n🌂行山杖 <br />\n<br />\n🚑🚑FA物品<br />\n🚨生理鹽水<br />\n🚨Gauze (紗布，4吋敷料，繃帶) .<br />\n<br />\n日常用品👕<br />\n✅背囊套，淨黑色帽，冰袖<br />\n✅大量口罩<br />\n✅黑色風褸，輕便衫<br />\n✅退熱貼，雨褸<br />\n✅細支消毒洗手液<br />\n✅紙巾，濕紙巾<br />\n✅彩色摺紙<br />\n✅3m噴膠(貼文宣)<br />\n<br />\n手足生活飯卷💰<br />\n💵惠康/百佳超市卷(買日常用品)<br />\n💵KFC/McDonald&rsquo;s/大家樂<br />\n💵鴻福堂現金卷/涼茶卷/湯卷<br />\n💵健康工坊涼茶卷/湯卷 💵八達通<br />\n💵唐記飯卷<br />\n💵書卷/衫褲鞋禮品卡.<br />\n<br />\n❌攻擊性武器❌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">🚸因為現時處於長期抗爭，物資消耗較快，所以物資會定期進行收集，家長有任何物資都可以捐畀我哋，以提供前線人員進行替換🙇🏻&zwj;♀🙇🏻&zwj;♀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n😊😊查詢詳情可訂閲《多元化》Channel: <br />\n⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>TG Channel:<a href=\"https://t.me/Peaceandlovehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FPeaceandlovehk&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2BsgxD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=133e3044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Peaceandlovehk</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Instag